{"tid":2163011,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【TVB】電視廣播與優酷達成戰略合作　進一步拓展內地市場","createTime":"2020-08-18T12:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T12:30:32.000Z","uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07b0a3bf59fd56af6d2fe65023fdf3d0b3eadb7a","tid":2163011,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:03:38.000Z","msg":"【TVB】電視廣播與優酷達成戰略合作 進一步拓展內地市場<br />\n 即市財經 15:34 2020/08/18 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2727747/%E3%80%90TVB%E3%80%91%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%BB%A3%E6%92%AD%E8%88%87%E5%84%AA%E9%85%B7%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%80%E9%80%B2%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2727747%2F%25E3%2580%2590TVB%25E3%2580%2591%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%2592%25AD%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2584%25AA%25E9%2585%25B7%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2588%2590%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2595%25A5%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%2580%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E6%258B%2593%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A0%25B4&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5kBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=b04215e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2727747/%E3%80%90TVB%E3%80%91%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%BB%A3%E6%92%AD%E8%88%87%E5%84%AA%E9%85%B7%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E3%80%80%E9%80%B2%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n電視廣播董事局主席許濤表示，是次合為公司的內容生產及區域市場發展帶來新的增長動力。<br />\n<br />\n電視廣播 （00511） 公布，與內地三大視頻平台之一優酷簽訂戰略合作協議，將在影視、綜藝、藝人、電子商貿、串流媒體平台等五大方面全力發展，鞏固公司於香港娛樂品牌的領導地位，進一步在內地建立具廣泛影響力的「新港味泛粵娛樂」產業和市場陣地。<br />\n<br />\nTVB董事局主席許濤表示，內容開發、藝人栽培、市場開拓、新商業模式探索等方面，雙方均具重大優勢及發揮互補作用。他表示，是次戰略合作的目標，是共同創造優勢的模塊組合，為TVB的內容生產及區域市場發展帶來新的增長動力。"},{"pid":"5c63d010cda2031e1105718fc31fae09644968a4","tid":2163011,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:04:54.000Z","msg":"電視廣播與優酷達成戰略合作協議<br />\n2020-08-18 HKT 14:42<br />\n <br />\n電視廣播與內地視頻平台優酷簽訂戰略合作協議，將在影視、綜藝、藝人、電子商貿、串流媒體平台等5大方向全力發展，進一步在內地建立「新港味泛粵娛樂」產業和市場陣地。<br />\n<br />\n主席許濤說，今次與優酷達成新的戰略合作，集團在影視領域將進一步開拓版權開發與發行、劇集及綜藝合拍、合製的空間；集團的內容IP與藝人資源會進一步與優酷的平台資源結合，在電商直播等新業務方面謀求新的突破和發展。<br />\n<br />\n電視廣播較早時報9.13元，升幅2.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544376-20200818.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544376-20200818.htm&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5kBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=7aed0633\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544376-20200818.htm&h=72dc3d94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544376-20200818.htm</a>"},{"pid":"edc6d11cc497e342b9f41a26827967181b21a899","tid":2163011,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:05:38.000Z","msg":"搬埋上走啦屌 篤眼篤鼻"},{"pid":"23db9b72f6a40cb70005e8a540c0d706481fb267","tid":2163011,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:06:46.000Z","msg":"將在影視、綜藝、藝人、電子商貿、串流媒體平台等5大方向全力發展，進一步在內地建立「<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">新港味泛粵娛樂</span></span></strong>」產業和市場陣地。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n腥梘味"},{"pid":"f90a2808822b3e9f209f9cae89a31864c5500861","tid":2163011,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:10:31.000Z","msg":